{
  "texts": [
    "The effect increases qualitatively along the ascending auditory pathway (for formal quantitative testing see Figure4).",
    "Responses to the remaining experimental conditions are shown in Supplementary FigureS2.",
    "Blue halves of the violin plots correspond to the left hemisphere; red halves to the right hemisphere.",
    "Violin plots are kernel density estimations across the entire population (one sample per participant).",
    "All p-values were computed using one-sided ranksum tests and Holm-Bonferroni corrected for 15 comparisons (nominal corrected and uncorrected p-values are listed in Supplementary TableS2)."
  ]
}